  <refnamediv>
    <refname>btkSetAnalogResolution</refname>
    <refpurpose>Set the ADC resolution</refpurpose>
  </refnamediv>
  <refsynopsisdiv>
    <title>Calling Sequence</title>
    <synopsis>btkSetAnalogResolution(h, res)</synopsis>
  </refsynopsisdiv>
  <refsection>
    <title>Parameters</title>
    <variablelist>
      <varlistentry>
        <term>h</term>
        <listitem><para>The handle used to represent an acquisition.</para></listitem>
      </varlistentry>
      <varlistentry>
        <term>res</term>
        <listitem><para>The new analog resolution. The value must be 8, 12, 14 or 16..</para></listitem>
      </varlistentry>
    </variablelist>
  </refsection>
  <refsection>
    <title>Description</title>
    <para>Set the resolution of the analog to digital converter.</para>
    <para>The acquisition is represented by the handle <literal>h</literal>. This handle is obtained  by the use of a btk* function.</para>
  </refsection>
  <refsection>
    <title>Examples</title>
    <programlisting role="example">btkSetAnalogResolution(h, 16)</programlisting>
  </refsection>
  <refsection>
    <title>See Also</title>
    <simplelist type="inline">
      <member>
        <link linkend="btkGetAnalogResolution">btkGetAnalogResolution</link>
      </member>
    </simplelist>
  </refsection>
</refentry>
